HEADWORD: Wavellite
<hw>Wa"vel*lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[After Dr. Wm.
<ets>Wavel</ets>, the discoverer.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A
